  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to demonstrate the influence of peri-operative nutrition on the
      post-operative complications, preservation of lean body mass and length of stay after
      gastrectomy or oesophagectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
